---
title: Fall Harvest Bowl Serves 2 | with Candied Pecans and Goat Cheese
description: Cozy up to this hearty bowl of roasted veggies, candied pecans and creamy goat cheese for a satisfying mid-day meal. It's all tossed in a shallot vinaigrette and finished with crispy bacon!
